<Layout title="About Patriot Discount Oil" description="Affordable heating oil delivery and expert furnace maintenance in Middletown and central Connecticut. Patriot Discount Oil offers top-quality service, emergency heating solutions, and unbeatable prices. Trusted since 2013." heading="The Best Heating Oil in Connecticut " >
<div class="flex flex-col mt-12">
<div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row ">
  <div class="md:w-1/2 m-auto p-4 max-w-[500px]">
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-start text-center font-black mb-2">We Are Summit</h1>
