    </p>
  </div>
  <img src="/teamphoto.png" alt="Summit Exteriors Rochester Roof Install" class="md:w-1/2 md:h-auto h-[300px]">
</div>



<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse my-12 ">
  
  <div class="md:w-1/2 m-auto p-4 max-w-[500px]">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black m-auto text-center mb-6">Our Mission</h1>
    <p>At Summit, we truly believe that satisfying our customers comes before all else. We have been serving the Rochester Community since 2016. As we grow the Summit family and brand, we constantly incorporate new industry leading technology to better suit our customers! When choosing a company to trust with the task of building your roof, there is no place that will put your best interest first like we will. Call our office today and we will partner one of our exterior designers with you, to guide you through this process.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="md:w-1/2">
    <img src="/SummitExteriorsRochesterRoofInstall.png" alt="Summit Exteriors Rochester Roof Install" class=" w-[500px] mx-auto">
